I've literally been with this kid all of my life. Met him at Fine Arts Dance Academy and has stuck by my side ever since. Yesterday was our 2nd and last concert together, time goes by so fast. I still remember when you came to the studio and you took @misschelle18 's class, months later we were all in our hip hop crew mini dbfad with our bright orange costume. And our dance battle at @breanna_hurd 's birthday party and your birthday party too. HA these are all things I will never forget. But the best part of it all was to watch you grow into an incredible friend, dancer, and role model. You've inspired me to always be the best I can be, and have shown me how to be a leader. You encourage me, give me great advice and are always there for me. For that I can never repay you. Although this is not the end of our friendship, dance battles, water & pasta, laughs, lunch dates, shopping trips, photoshoots, dancing, and laughs .... I'm extremely proud of you and can't wait to watch you grow into the person you want to be. I love you so much and I'm extremely grateful for you jonny! 💜💙💛❤️ #queenphooda #inches @jonnyestradaa
